    dc:description "FIGURES 6 – 9. Tropizodium peregrinum n. gen., n. sp. 6. Female, habitus; 7. Female, lateral view; 8. Prosoma, ventral view; 9. Prosoma, frontal view. (scale lines: 0.5 mm)" ;
