<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.171180>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 5. Tropizodium peregrinum n. gen., n. sp. Scanning electron micrographs. 1. femoral organ on leg II of female, dorsolateral view; 2. chelicerae, ventral view; 3. Female right palpal tarsus, dorsal view showing distal toothed claw turned inwards over 45 ° and modified setae; 4. male right palp, retrolateral view; 5. Median apophysis, prolateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/171180/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

